BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:Ij-japZzk5ynJveVomiav
SUMMARY:Show Your Game: An Improvised Game Show
DTSTAMP:20260301T153242Z
DTSTART:20260301T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:In Show Your Game\\\, professional improvisers and fearless aud
	ience volunteers step into the worlds of real-life experts and attempt to 
	survive challenges designed by those experts. Expect strange trivia\\\, im
	possible tasks\\\, wildly specific knowledge\\\, and the kind of confidenc
	e that only comes from being completely wrong in public. \\nMaybe it’s acu
	puncture. Maybe it’s panic packing. Maybe it’s Gilmore Girls. Maybe it’s f
	inding creative new places to lose your keys. \\nInspired by the chaotic b
	rilliance of Taskmaster\\\, the clever curiosity of QI\\\, and the unpredi
	ctable madness of Game Changer\\\, every show is completely improvised and
	 completely different. \\nPast topics have included haunting\\\, bubbles\\
	\, bedtime routines\\\, public art\\\, computer programming\\\, low-income
	 housing\\\, tabletop RPG streaming\\\, Veggie Tales\\\, housesitting disa
	sters\\\, and one unforgettable investigation into a single person’s missi
	ng keys. \\nYou might learn something. You will absolutely laugh. \\nSoone
	r or later… It’s your turn to Show Your Game. your turn to step into someo
	ne else’s world… are you ready to Show Your Game?\n\nhttps://www.unexpecte
	dproductions.org/event/show-your-game-an-improvised-game-show-2/\n\nFrom U
	nexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/show-your-game-an-improvise
	d-game-show-2/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
END:VEVENT
